[Russia's last HPAI update was sent to the OIE on 16 Feb 2006; see
<http://www.oie.int/eng/info/hebdo/AIS_30.HTM#Sec2>. The above press release
might be regarded as a temporary available official update. Since its
publication, the press informed suspected new outbreaks in 2 Siberian
territories, namely the Tuva republic and the Tomsk region (map at
<http://www.eegas.com/images/11-legend.gif>). So far, no confirmation from
the reference laboratory has been available. - Mod.AS]
